    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class Min
extends ExtremaBase
    Class Min is an Aggregator that returns the minimum value encountered in the current group. *

    This class assumes the argument values is a Number, or a String representation of a number.

    See MinValue to find the min of any Comparable type.
